WEBVTT

00:10.227 --> 00:12.403
Previously onOne Dollar...

00:12.447 --> 00:15.798
CHELSEA: I grew up with a liar.
So I'm just...

00:15.841 --> 00:19.628
done, you know, being a mark.

00:19.671 --> 00:22.065
You done creeping around
people's windows for the night?

00:22.109 --> 00:23.545
Decided to creep on me?

00:23.588 --> 00:25.242
What are you doing here?

00:25.286 --> 00:26.983
Maybe it's time I finally met
my granddaughter.

00:27.027 --> 00:28.680
That's not fucking happening.

00:28.724 --> 00:29.986
JULIE: I'm beginning to think
you're more interested

00:30.030 --> 00:31.466
in replacing his wife

00:31.509 --> 00:34.121
than figuring out
if maybe he murdered her.

00:34.164 --> 00:36.775
